# Phase 10 lineup/event blobs — large generated data, minified by the sync
# writer (writeJsonStableMin). Prettier must NOT reformat them: it would inflate
# the committed size ~2x AND break the cron's idempotent diff (sync writes
# minified, prettier rewrites pretty → noise PR every run).
data/lineups-*.json
data/events-*.json

# Cross-season search index — written by writeJsonStable (each array element on
# its own line), but prettier inlines short arrays (e.g. "aliases": ["laca"]).
# That format drift breaks the cron's idempotent diff (sync rewrites multi-line
# → noise PR every run) and used to require a manual `git checkout` after every
# commit. writeJsonStable owns this file's formatting; prettier must not touch it.
data/search-index.json

# TASK-1606 Arabic-name sidecar maps — written by the build/apply scripts via
